{"type": "article", "id": 13436, "title": "Sphero 机器人 2.0 版本", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-13T07:31:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 35, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702125740IOrRqmw6eazC39Jt.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t培养程序员要从娃娃抓起。Sphero 机器人现在推出了 2.0 版本，这是一款专门为小孩设计的机器人，移栽激发孩子的编程兴趣，锻炼编程能力。小球带有专门开发的 Sphero SPRK 应用程序和 OVAL 语言，小孩子对其进行简单的编程，可以调整小球的颜色，速度等参数，打造属于他们自己的小球，同时在玩乐中体验“开发者”的角色，激发开发的潜力和兴趣。目前产品售价 130 美元，这是<a href=\"http://sphero.com/\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141217gIKL1PC6JqjQW2ci.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261412188M0o5Ozy6qjrVcwm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141218yQ7iLRvEfxOk85X4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141219RxJaVL2ZkqXwPCcg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141219IY5TcbZXzNMe3DCE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141220xr0cfnpIDuM6itQ7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141220rKFe0PMXiwVUvdok.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141221gFuq8wasVOyPWfo4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141221yFcSs9Qw8XTNgC43.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}